list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Note: This is my first commit and push to GitHub.
These are Java classes that represent different people and things considered when a school assigns courses to its students. Students, teachers, courses, course sections, times, and rooms are considered. The Hungarian Algorithm is used to assign one group to another group, through functionality for multi-dimensional assignment is missing.
